# Listing Google Compute Engine resources in descending order by age

I was working a support case where the customer asked how they could list Compute Engine Instnaces in descending order by time of creaiton. 
While this is a cery straightforward question, there are many ways we can go about doing this. 

The Cloud Console menu for Compute Engine allows you to filter by creation time. We will learn how to do it using gcloud, and various other methods.

